===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[bunch]] of [[feather]]s, [[grass]] or [[hair]], etc., held together at the [[base]].
# A [[cluster]] of [[thread]]s drawn tightly through [[upholstery]], a [[mattress]] or a [[quilt]], etc., to [[secure]] and [[strengthen]] the [[padding]].
# A small [[clump]] of [[tree]]s or [[bush]]es.
# {{context|formerly}} A gold [[tassel]] on the cap worn by [[titled]] [[undergraduate]]s at English universities.
# A person [[entitle]]d to wear such a tassel.

